<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 10:08:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>世界谴责以色列对拉法的“可怕的、不公正的”袭击；要求国际法院作出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/eu-israel-continues-military-action-despite-icj-order-u-s-looks-into-rafah-attack/0000018f-b89e-df13-a3af-bc9ef6450000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告称，加沙流离失所者的帐篷遭到袭击，造成 35 人死亡；以色列军队声称袭击目标是哈马斯官员，并表示正在审查有关“无关个人”遭到袭击的报道；欧盟最高外交官要求以色列执行国际法院对拉法的裁决</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 06:42:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/eu-israel-continues-military-action-despite-icj-order-u-s-looks-into-rafah-attack/0000018f-b89e-df13-a3af-bc9ef6450000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人：以色列袭击拉法帐篷造成数十人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯官员被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-report-at-least-35-killed-by-israeli-strikes-on-displaced-area-in-rafah/0000018f-b80a-d24f-a5df-feee2ae40007</link><description>以色列国防军首席律师：拉法事件“非常严重”；以色列国防军警方发起约 70 项调查，包括针对斯德泰曼监狱设施的调查 ■ 白宫关于拉法袭击：了解报道，收集更多信息 ■ 巴勒斯坦权力机构：以色列对拉法的袭击“跨越所有边界”，呼吁国际社会立即干预 ■ 以色列国防军宣布两名士兵死亡 ■ 战时内阁召开会议讨论人质交易</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-report-at-least-35-killed-by-israeli-strikes-on-displaced-area-in-rafah/0000018f-b80a-d24f-a5df-feee2ae40007</guid></item><item><title>国防部长加兰特批评甘茨支持正统军队豁免法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-criticizes-gantz-for-support-of-haredi-army-exemption-law/0000018f-b720-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e10e70000</link><description>加兰特说，正统派政党的代表告诉他，内阁成员本尼·甘茨表示，他支持该法案的条件是他们同意提前选举。甘茨否认所有说法，称正统党派退出谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:12:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-criticizes-gantz-for-support-of-haredi-army-exemption-law/0000018f-b720-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e10e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察与犹太信徒在梅龙山庆祝活动中发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-jewish-worshippers-clash-at-mt-meron-celebration/0000018f-b61e-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e1c4e0000</link><description>尽管由于真主党的袭击，该地点已被宣布为军事禁区，但仍有数千人参加 Lag Ba&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动；视频显示一名警察将一名老人推倒在地</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-jewish-worshippers-clash-at-mt-meron-celebration/0000018f-b61e-d7ed-a7ef-bf3e1c4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军人质负责人：我们绝望了，不会与这个政府达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/idf-hostage-chief-we-are-desperate-there-will-be-no-deal-with-this-government/0000018f-b609-d24f-a5df-feef59780000</link><description>据第 12 频道报道，这位负责人表示，“我推动的协议将包括归还所有人质，而哈马斯则坚称这将包括结束战争”。内塔尼亚胡：“谈判团队内部的冲突只会加强哈马斯的地位”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:36:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/idf-hostage-chief-we-are-desperate-there-will-be-no-deal-with-this-government/0000018f-b609-d24f-a5df-feef59780000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的忠诚者在以色列内战的道路上创造了另一个里程碑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-loyalists-spawn-another-milestone-on-the-path-to-civil-war-in-israel/0000018f-b5ef-dca9-a5cf-b5ef4f370000</link><description>是否有任何预备役人员组织等待内塔尼亚胡的命令，即使下达撤退命令，仍继续在加沙作战？几乎可以肯定不是，即使有，这个视频也不能证明这一点。但让以色列人担心情况可能会是这样，这对内塔尼亚胡和极右翼来说是有利的</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:15:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-loyalists-spawn-another-milestone-on-the-path-to-civil-war-in-israel/0000018f-b5ef-dca9-a5cf-b5ef4f370000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加哈南·亚布隆卡的葬礼队伍，其尸体从加沙被打捞上来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/thousands-join-funeral-procession-for-hostage-whose-body-was-retrieved-from-gaza/0000018f-b5de-d24f-a5df-fffef00b0000</link><description>家人将这次葬礼定为人质家属的希望游行，许多参与者都系着黄丝带前来。亚布隆卡的母亲赞叹道：“这不是我想要的结局，但至少你回到了我们身边。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/thousands-join-funeral-procession-for-hostage-whose-body-was-retrieved-from-gaza/0000018f-b5de-d24f-a5df-fffef00b0000</guid></item><item><title>研究表明，喝咖啡因的蚂蚁可能会产生更好的蚂蚁陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-26/ty-article/ants-on-caffeine-could-lead-to-a-better-ant-trap-study-suggests/0000018f-b578-dca9-a5cf-b57893940000</link><description>这正是我们一直想要的：具有卓越学习能力的嗡嗡作响的觅食蚂蚁。但一项新的研究表明，这可能会导致更好的、含有咖啡因的蚂蚁陷阱</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 17:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-26/ty-article/ants-on-caffeine-could-lead-to-a-better-ant-trap-study-suggests/0000018f-b578-dca9-a5cf-b57893940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 233 天：以色列国防军终止呼吁叛变的男子的预备役服役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-233-idf-terminates-reserve-service-of-man-who-called-for-mutiny/0000018f-b5ca-d33c-a5bf-ffdb20d70001</link><description>哈马斯自 1 月以来首次对以色列中部发动攻击 ■ 据 CNN 报道，释放人质/停火协议谈判将于周二恢复 ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨提出建议，成立一个调查委员会，调查 10 月 7 日和加沙战争 ■ 大约 200 辆援助卡车通过与以色列接壤的凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点进入加沙 ■ 战争进入 233 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-233-idf-terminates-reserve-service-of-man-who-called-for-mutiny/0000018f-b5ca-d33c-a5bf-ffdb20d70001</guid></item><item><title>“丑闻”：西班牙外长就“哈马斯感谢西班牙”视频回击以色列外长卡茨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/outrageous-spanish-fm-lashes-out-at-israeli-counterpart-katz-over-gracias-hamas-video/0000018f-b5b7-d33c-a5bf-ffb75e560000</link><description>在西班牙宣布承认巴勒斯坦国后，以色列外交部长以色列卡茨在 X 上发布了一段短视频，称“哈马斯：西班牙之恩”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/outrageous-spanish-fm-lashes-out-at-israeli-counterpart-katz-over-gracias-hamas-video/0000018f-b5b7-d33c-a5bf-ffb75e560000</guid></item><item><title>犹太纽约人纠结是否参加今年的以色列日游行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/jewish-new-yorkers-wrestle-with-whether-to-march-in-this-years-israel-day-parade/0000018f-b491-dfc6-a3ef-b5ddd2540000</link><description>被扣押在加沙的人质代表定于 6 月 2 日游行，但广受诟病的内塔尼亚胡政府的四名成员也将游行 — — 让许多外籍以色列人和自由派犹太人陷入困境</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/jewish-new-yorkers-wrestle-with-whether-to-march-in-this-years-israel-day-parade/0000018f-b491-dfc6-a3ef-b5ddd2540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-combat-last-week/0000018f-b59a-d08f-adcf-b7fa97b80000</link><description>中士。 20 岁的贝扎莱尔·兹维·科瓦奇 (Betzalel Zvi Kovach) 上周三在加沙北部受伤，并于周日因伤死亡。中士。 20 岁的 Sahar Sudaei 周日在加沙北部被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-combat-last-week/0000018f-b59a-d08f-adcf-b7fa97b80000</guid></item><item><title>舒默参议员，不要邀请内塔尼亚胡。他不是你的盟友或朋友。他从来都不是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</link><description>向以色列坚定的民主党盟友传达的信息：不要邀请本杰明·内塔尼亚胡参加国会。他的唯一目的是在执行特朗普的命令时破坏美国总统乔·拜登的连任竞选</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 15:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</guid></item><item><title>1956 年以色列巴勒斯坦村庄发生的大屠杀被搬上银幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/the-1956-massacre-that-haunts-a-palestinian-village-in-israel-makes-it-to-the-screen/0000018f-ab36-d24f-a5df-fff6e5170000</link><description>同样在本周的文化综述中：一位艺术家讲述了她的父母被绑架到加沙的故事，获得了大奖； 《加沙之美》在戛纳备受争议；穆斯拉拉混合唤醒了耶路撒冷；穆罕默德·阿博·萨尔姆 (Muhammad Abo Salme) 为特拉维夫带来一线光明</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 15:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/the-1956-massacre-that-haunts-a-palestinian-village-in-israel-makes-it-to-the-screen/0000018f-ab36-d24f-a5df-fff6e5170000</guid></item><item><title>“这只是一次公关活动”：爱尔兰总统驳斥了爱尔兰反犹太主义的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/simply-a-pr-exercise-irish-president-belittles-claims-of-antisemitism-in-ireland/0000018f-b511-d24f-a5df-fff766580000</link><description>以色列驻爱尔兰大使发表了有关打击爱尔兰反犹太主义的声明，希金斯总统立即谴责该声明“不负责任”。 “爱尔兰人并不反犹太主义，”他辩称，并接着提到前任总统说希伯来语</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/simply-a-pr-exercise-irish-president-belittles-claims-of-antisemitism-in-ireland/0000018f-b511-d24f-a5df-fff766580000</guid></item><item><title>停止！现在！我们以色列士兵的母亲要求结束加沙徒劳的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/stop-now-we-mothers-of-israeli-soldiers-demand-an-end-to-the-futile-war-in-gaza/0000018f-b3c9-d390-ab8f-f3c9fa920000</link><description>我是以色列国防军士兵家长运动的一部分，他们曾经支持这场战争，但现在反对这场战争，这场战争已成为我们孩子毫无意义的死亡陷阱，一场由不愿结束的极端主义政府领导的战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/stop-now-we-mothers-of-israeli-soldiers-demand-an-end-to-the-futile-war-in-gaza/0000018f-b3c9-d390-ab8f-f3c9fa920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军警调查预备役军人呼吁加沙大规模反抗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-police-investigating-reservist-calling-for-mass-insubordination-in-gaza/0000018f-b466-d24f-a5df-fee668820000</link><description>警方确认视频中的嫌疑人是来自荷兹利亚的预备役军人，并表示他们已将他带去接受审问。该视频在社交媒体上广泛传播，总理的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡也被广泛转发，视频声称 10 万名以色列国防军预备役军人不服从离开加沙的命令</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-police-investigating-reservist-calling-for-mass-insubordination-in-gaza/0000018f-b466-d24f-a5df-fee668820000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日最后一刻的战斗从哈马斯手中拯救了 12 条生命</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-last-minute-october-7-battle-that-saved-the-lives-of-12-thai-workers/0000018f-a973-df13-a3af-bd77230c0000</link><description>10月7日，哈马斯恐怖分子在梅法西姆基布兹抓获12名泰国工人后，他们的上司到处寻找他们。他们最终被以色列安全部队救出，然后被绑架到加沙</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 13:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-last-minute-october-7-battle-that-saved-the-lives-of-12-thai-workers/0000018f-a973-df13-a3af-bd77230c0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯数月来首次从拉法向以色列中部特拉维夫发射火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fires-rocket-barrage-from-rafah-at-tel-aviv-central-israel-for-first-time-in-months/0000018f-b4bb-d24f-a5df-feff56040000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，弹幕是从拉法发射的，哈马斯很快承认对火箭弹负责。以色列中部城市多枚火箭弹碎片落下，荷兹利亚一户住宅的屋顶被落下的火箭弹片损坏</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 13:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fires-rocket-barrage-from-rafah-at-tel-aviv-central-israel-for-first-time-in-months/0000018f-b4bb-d24f-a5df-feff56040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电影制片人用原始镜头与 10 月 7 日否认者作斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-film-producer-fighting-october-7-deniers/0000018f-a5d9-d1e2-a1ff-afff06390000</link><description>在制作了两部关于哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的纪录片之后，制作公司首席执行官梅尼·阿维拉姆 (Meny Aviram) 表示，他意识到必须立即讲述这个故事，并为未来保留更多纪录片</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-film-producer-fighting-october-7-deniers/0000018f-a5d9-d1e2-a1ff-afff06390000</guid></item></channel></rss>